  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to be notified if a transaction was confirmed or failed **so that** I can be sure if the transaction succeeds or not while doing another task within the Status app\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nFigma Design: https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=2402-511527&mode=design&t=aTiN1IeemgbJnFPl-4\r\n\r\nVisual reference:\r\n<img width=\"282\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/18485527/9a78cfb6-9f8a-45fe-ac96-dbc8334ce148\">\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- [ ] Notification can be dismissed by swiping up on it\r\n- [ ] If user taps on the notification, Transaction Status screen should be opened",
